% ramalama-perplexity 1

## NAME
ramalama\-perplexity - calculate the perplexity value of an AI Model

## SYNOPSIS
**ramalama perplexity** [*options*] *model* [arg ...]

@@include options/model-transports.md

## OPTIONS

@@option authfile

@@option backend

@@option cache-reuse

@@option ctx-size

@@option device

@@option env

@@option help

@@option image

@@option keep-groups

@@option max-tokens

@@option name

@@option network

@@option ngl

@@option oci-runtime

@@option privileged

@@option pull

@@option runtime-args

@@option seed

@@option selinux

@@option temp

@@option threads

@@option tls-verify

## DESCRIPTION
Calculate the perplexity of an AI Model. Perplexity measures how well the model can predict the next token with lower values being better.

## EXAMPLES

```
ramalama perplexity granite3-moe
```

